---
title: Mexican Bacon & Corn Fritters with Fries, Cucumber Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet, and are set off perfectly by an A-team of creamy mayo and
cucumber slaw, fries and smokey aioli. If you fancy it, you could also break out your favourite hot sauce for these bad boys!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6502c42afb7ac5e0bcadef86-cae6253a.jpeg
